text: Veronica Grymonprez (born 17 January 1944) is a Belgian gymnast. She competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Berlin
